Package hotciv.framework

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    City
    Represents a city in the game.
    Game
    Game is the central interface allowing a client to access and modify the state of a HotCiv game.
    GameObserver
    Defines the Observer role for a Game.
    Tile
    Tile represents a single territory tile of a given type.
    Unit
    Represents a single unit in the game.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GameConstants
    Collection of constants used in HotCiv Game.
    Position
    Position on the world map.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Player
    Represents a player of the game.
